campaignevents-event-details-participant: Dikarabo tsa batsayakarolo ka bongwe ka bngwe di phimotswe mme dikarabo tse di kopantsweng di teng ka fa tlase ga [ $1 {{int:ditiragalo tsa letsholo-dintlha-tsa-tiragalo-thebo-dipalopalo}}].
